          GraphicInterface _graphicInterface
          The graphic interface object is an instance of the containing class, called when messages are typed from the user and will call this thread to display messages.

        • _title

          java.lang.String _title
          The title object is the title of the window.

        • _ip

          java.lang.String _ip
          The ip object will define the target ip that this client window is for.

        • _channel

          java.lang.String _channel
          The channel object defines the target channel that this client window is for. If the channel is set to 'private' it is for direct messaging.

        • txtrDisplayArea

          javax.swing.JTextArea txtrDisplayArea
          Text display area displays the chat history with the client.

        • scrollPaneDisplayArea

          javax.swing.JScrollPane scrollPaneDisplayArea
          The scroll pane display area allows the chat history to be scrollable.

        • _thread

          java.lang.Thread _thread
          The thread object handles the threading of the display window.
